20:11.577 --> 20:14.447 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Lisa Desjardins looks at the big
questions
ahead.

20:14.480 --> 20:19.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: One major
issue: the health
of the marketplaces for
individuals who get

20:19.785 --> 20:21.454 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
