average of 25
percent this year.

20:26.225 --> 20:27.693 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What's happening?

20:27.726 --> 20:32.298 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In part, the exchanges need more
younger and
healthier adults to enroll.

20:32.331 --> 20:36.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Our team has been fanning out
across the country
to hear about Americans'
concerns.

20:36.135 --> 20:41.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We start with a small business
in Salt Lake
City, and younger adults who are
not buying

20:41.173 --> 20:42.374 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
coverage now.

20:42.408 --> 20:44.643 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PATRICIA SMITH, Salt Lake City:
My name is
Patricia Smith.

20:44.677 --> 20:48.714 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm 33 years old, and I'm the
manager at Camp
Bow Wow.

20:48.747 --> 20:52.918 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
