40:04.802 --> 40:06.571 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Is this something Republicans
can learn how
to be, in the majority, in
charge?

40:06.604 --> 40:11.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Well,
