41:25.149 --> 41:26.951 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: For sure.

41:26.984 --> 41:30.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, Tam, I mean, this brings to
mind, while
the Republicans are trying to
figure out what

41:30.388 --> 41:35.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
